Class QAT54_CaseConfiguration5Test

    QAT-RRD-Automate Case Configuration 5

    1.Login into RRD application

    2.Go to SetUp page

    4.Click on App launcher

    5.Search RRD and clicks on The searched Iption RRD that directed to RRD Application Home page

    3.Click on step1Configuration tab

    4.Navigate to iframe.

    5.click on edit button.

    6.Select user from drop down value that is All.

    7.Select owner notification from drop down value that is by email.

    8.Select Relationship based assignment value from drop down that is None.

    9.Uncheck Queue assignment checkbox

    10.Uncheck handle manual assignment checkbox

    11.Uncheck Handle High Priority Case Checkbox

    12.click on save button to save data

    13.Assert that Case config changes has saved By checking if Edit button is visble

    Author:
    Manas Jena
